rentals.Name: 1x1
rentals.Description:
Be the first to live in these stunning, newly renovated apartments in the heart of Golden Hill!

Receive $1500 off your second month's rent!!

This beautiful, spacious 1-bedrooms/1-bath unit on the 1st floor is available to move in NOW! It has large windows with great city views and a wall-to-wall walk-in closet to store all of your essentials.

To schedule a tour today, please call/text Deb...Contact the property to learn more about this unit.

Gorgeous 1 bedroom 1 bath condo in the heart of downtown. Prime location! Easy access from freeways, walking distance to restaurants, bars, shopping, and supermarket. Building has a security guard, fitness center, bbq area, roof top with jacuzzi. Washer & Dryer in unit. 10 minutes to the Airport. Walking distance to trolley. 1 parking space. Fully furnished. All utilities are included SDG&E has $150 CAP. Short & Long term options. Min. 30 days rental. Available NOW!

Introducing Radian, the epitome of luxury living in downtown San Diego's Ballpark District. With a prime location just 2 blocks north of Petco Park, this 22-story high-rise offers over 240 available exquisite 1-3 bedroom units and penthouse suites, starting from $3,000. Imagine waking up to panoramic views of the city and Petco Park, with the sun cascading through floor-to-ceiling windows onto your Italian cabinetry kitchen. This is the reality at Radian, a 22-story luxury apartment oasis in the heart of San Diego's thriving Ballpark District. Radian's allure lies in its unparalleled 360Â° views, striking interiors, environmentally conscious design and engaging social spaces. Each residence is a testament to modern luxury, featuring floor-to-ceiling windows, Italian kitchen cabinetry, waterfall quartz countertops, walk-in closets, lit mirror bathroom vanities, built-in quartz countertop desks, and luxury smart appliances. Beyond the lavish interiors, Radian boasts an impressive array of community amenities. Residents can bask on the rooftop, which has direct views into Petco Parkâ€™s stadium, at the resort-style pool with cabanas, savor the rooftop BBQs and pizza oven, or make use of the clubhouse with a remote work suite. Fitness enthusiasts will appreciate the indoor/outdoor fitness center and yoga room, while pet owners will delight in the barc parc and dog spa. With private access to the community and parking garage, convenience is paramount. *Prices and amenities vary per unit. Please consult the onsite agent for details on the unit in question.

Step into city life with this fully furnished 6th-floor, 2-bedroom, 2-bath south-facing loft-style property in the heart of San Diego's East Village. Featuring a bright, inviting layout with two bedrooms, this home is located in the M2i building, making it ideal for those wanting to be close to all the downtown buzz. It's just a short walk from the vibrant Gaslamp District and a block from Petco Park. As you enter, the abundance of natural light from the floor-to-ceiling windows instantly makes the space feel open and welcoming. The stunning city views can be fully appreciated or easily hidden for privacy with remote-controlled blinds. The open-plan living area seamlessly merges with a modern kitchen, creating the perfect setting for both entertaining and quiet evenings. The master bedroom offers an ensuite bathroom and features a large walk-in closet, providing ample storage. The balcony is your private space to relax and enjoy the urban scenery.This property includes two secure, tandem underground parking spaces conveniently located near the elevators, adding ease and security for your vehicles. Its location places you at the heart of San Diego's finest dining, shopping, and entertainment within the lively East Village. With an array of cafes, shops, and cultural spots to explore, there's always something exciting to do. Amenities feature a well-equipped gym, a 7th-floor rooftop lounge ideal for gatherings, offering panoramic views, a BBQ area, a landscaped zen courtyard, and convenient bike storage.

Stunning 'fully built-out' upper floor two bedroom, two bath loft with dramatic 11' ceilings, oversized windows with fabulous city views. Newly remodeled floor,  kitchen cabinets, light fixtures and bathroom.  Luxury loft style exposed cement walls, walk-in closets, European cabinetry with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Located in the heart of East Village/Ball park district in the M2i building and enjoy modern downtown luxury living at it's finest. Amenities include, gym, rooftop entertainment deck, BBQs and courtyard.
